CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 19, 1939. pg. 5, reads: "YOUTH TAKES A FLING in WATER - Helen Douglas [Douglass], Bob Anderson and Marian Stanton come up for air at South Park at the swimming party for Marva Louis. The young set had quite a time at this affair staged by Sports Eddy Ches. Washington. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Helen Douglass, Bob Anderson, and Marian Stanton holding on to side of swimming pool
